Founded in 2010 and composed of some senior technicians who have deep love for moble technology, Antutu Labs concentrates on delivering simple and accurate smart device benchmarking app. Our mission is to develop useful software which can make people have deep understanding to their mobile devices. AnTuTu Benchmark supports more ten languages including English, Russian, Japanese, Korean, Poland, Italian, Czech and so on. Nowadays, over 100,000,000 users used Antutu Benchmark. Antutu Benchmark has became a benchmark standard to mobile device users.

There are three possible reason:
1.No network connection during testing.

3.AnTuTu's network connection has been blocked by system or software.
Android virtual machine is the majority of application run mode, represent the overall performance.
The highest integer performance of the single core of CPU, a lot of apps only can use one CPU core.
The highest float performance of the single core of CPU, a lot of apps only can use one CPU core.
The highest integer performance of the entire CPU, integer arithmetic are used in the encrypting, compression/decompression etc.
The highest float performance of the entire CPU, float arithmetic are used in the image-processing, audio decoding etc.
RAM speed performance, test the highest speed that apps read and write in RAM.
RAM operation performance, test the highest performance that apps do operations in RAM.
Multi task performance, simulation multiple background apps running and switch etc.
Database I/O performance, test the database query, add, delete operational performance.
Storage I/O performance, test the performance of read and write in internal storage.
